  "detailed_description": "Gobsmacked is about riding a wave of chaos as you smash, tear, & shoot your way through waves of procedurally generated gladiator arenas, performing for adoring fans.  It's the fast-paced mini-FPS roguelite you’ve always dreamed of getting your gobliny claws on. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769410/extras/5405fd9422cce075c96cff3fd257277a.avif?t=1754141617\" width=610 height=80 /></span><br>You are a furry, frenetic, sensationally stylish goblin. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769410/extras/c737bee6eea57f1c2cc6ce414aa8696e.poster.avif?t=1754141617\" width=610 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769410/extras/c737bee6eea57f1c2cc6ce414aa8696e.webm?t=1754141617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769410/extras/c737bee6eea57f1c2cc6ce414aa8696e.mp4?t=1754141617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769410/extras/3767e7ff7c13edc812cc021f106bda40.avif?t=1754141617\" width=610 height=80 /></span> <br>Spend your cash on permanent gear you can equip at the start of a run, or arena upgrades to make the run you're on easier. Will you upgrade your flamethrower to bounce off walls or upgrade your melee attacks to explode on impact?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769410/extras/0e1639abe31bcc2db08c94016702500a.poster.avif?t=1754141617\" width=610 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769410/extras/0e1639abe31bcc2db08c94016702500a.webm?t=1754141617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769410/extras/0e1639abe31bcc2db08c94016702500a.mp4?t=1754141617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769410/extras/ffd7d8f01d90ac97e55435df8e22ff59.avif?t=1754141617\" width=610 height=80 /></span><br>Grapple, glide, double-jump, climb & stomp your way to victory. Gobsmacked is all about momentum and verticality.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769410/extras/091bd029fa9cc8f05a67c32c0f121ada.poster.avif?t=1754141617\" width=610 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769410/extras/091bd029fa9cc8f05a67c32c0f121ada.webm?t=1754141617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769410/extras/091bd029fa9cc8f05a67c32c0f121ada.mp4?t=1754141617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769410/extras/fb451ebcf9e048882756226006f1557a.avif?t=1754141617\" width=610 height=80 /></span> <br>Put on a show to entertain the crowds; they determine your rewards.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769410/extras/29b25da0e6dce47df7b6937ecd286f14.poster.avif?t=1754141617\" width=610 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769410/extras/29b25da0e6dce47df7b6937ecd286f14.webm?t=1754141617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769410/extras/29b25da0e6dce47df7b6937ecd286f14.mp4?t=1754141617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769410/extras/26ced2c7427237bfaad38aa6c5138f6f.avif?t=1754141617\" width=610 height=80 /></span> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769410/extras/0704c355fd3452362e94a16f2a92c68d.poster.avif?t=1754141617\" width=610 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769410/extras/0704c355fd3452362e94a16f2a92c68d.webm?t=1754141617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769410/extras/0704c355fd3452362e94a16f2a92c68d.mp4?t=1754141617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769410/extras/f541af46eadaf257cd5661e15db75526.avif?t=1754141617\" width=610 height=80 /></span> <br>Gobsmacked is fully physically simulated. You can snatch, throw, kick and gleefully wreck almost anything you can see.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769410/extras/21dbd8ad554f40b60c96f1b6ae8a21f1.poster.avif?t=1754141617\" width=610 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769410/extras/21dbd8ad554f40b60c96f1b6ae8a21f1.webm?t=1754141617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2769410/extras/21dbd8ad554f40b60c96f1b6ae8a21f1.mp4?t=1754141617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></vid